OL,3,CCoventry mother given suspended
OL,4,Csentence for helping son flee after
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA woman who helped her son leave the
OL,8,FUK after he murdered a "kind and
OL,9,Floving" father from Coventry, has been
OL,10,Fsentenced.
OL,12,FFaye Gowdy gave her son Ashley Donald
OL,13,Fmoney and brought him plane tickets to
OL,14,Fhelp him flee to Ireland, after he had
OL,15,Fhit Andrew Flamson while driving.
OL,17,FMr Flamson, 40, died after he was hit
OL,18,Fby a Mondeo following a row about a
OL,19,Fdrug debt on Grosvenor Road in July
OL,20,F2022.
