OL,3,CCoventry mother given suspended
OL,4,Csentence for helping son flee after
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDriver Ashley Donald was given a life
OL,8,Fsentence for murder last year.
OL,10,FGowdy was given a 24-month suspended
OL,11,Fsentence.
OL,13,FIn August this year, Bethany Donohue,
OL,14,Fof Albany Road in Coventry, was jailed
OL,15,Ffor three years for helping her then-
OL,16,Fboyfriend Donald try to evade capture.
