OL,7,FPolice said that they had started the
OL,8,Fprocess to extradite Donald, but he
OL,9,Freturned to the UK in September and
OL,10,Fhanded himself in at Coventry Police
OL,11,FStation.
OL,13,FOfficers arrested Gowdy at her home in
OL,14,FEdgbaston and Donohue when she landed
OL,15,Fback in the UK at Birmingham Airport.
OL,17,FDonald was jailed for life for murder
OL,18,Fafter Andrew Flamson died of head
OL,19,Finjuries three days after being
OL,20,Fknocked down by Donald. He was walking
OL,21,Fhis dog at the time.
